#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.25"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.25:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Bhāravagga "
msgstr "3. The Burden "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Chandarāgasutta "
msgstr "25. Desire and Greed "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.25:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.25:1.2"
msgid "“Yo, bhikkhave, rūpasmiṃ chandarāgo taṃ pajahatha. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, give up desire and greed for form. "

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.3"
msgid "Evaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ anabhāvaṃkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhammaṃ. "
msgstr "Thus that form will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.25:1.4"
msgid "Yo vedanāya chandarāgo taṃ pajahatha. "
msgstr "Give up desire and greed for feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.5"
msgid "Evaṃ sā vedanā pahīnā bhavissati ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā anabhāvaṃkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.6"
msgid "Yo saññāya chandarāgo taṃ pajahatha. "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.7"
msgid "Evaṃ sā saññā pahīnā bhavissati ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā anabhāvaṃkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.8"
msgid "Yo saṅkhāresu chandarāgo taṃ pajahatha. "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.9"
msgid "Evaṃ te saṅkhārā pahīnā bhavissanti ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā anabhāvaṃkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.10"
msgid "Yo viññāṇasmiṃ chandarāgo taṃ pajahatha. "
msgstr "consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.11"
msgid "Evaṃ taṃ viññāṇaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ anabhāvaṃkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhamman”ti. "
msgstr "Thus that consciousness will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.25:1.12"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
